- set_meta_tags title: 'Fund Raising', description: 'Whether you are raising money from venture capital, angel investors, banks, financial institutions, PE funds, IPO, Excide advises you as a virtual CFO does.', reverse: true
section.text-center.imagebg.space--lg data-overlay="3"
  .background-image-holder
    img.background-image alt="image" src=image_path('tall-skyscraper.jpg')
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.col-lg-12
        h1.type--uppercase Fund Raising
        h4 When you are raising money, Excide can advise you as a virtual CFO
        ol.breadcrumbs
          li
            a href="/"  Home
          li
            a href="/financial-analytics-reporting/"  Virtual Financial Officer
          li Fund Raising
section
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12
        .text-center
          h3.mb-5.type--uppercase Need to raise funds for your company?
        p.lead.m32.pb32 A fund raising exercise is a monetary injection into the company through interested investors. Such possible options for fundraising is from venture capital, angel investors, banks, financial institutions, PE funds and IPO.
section.pt240.pb240.imagebg.height-50
  .background-image-holder
    img.background-image alt="image" src=image_path('seminar-room.jpg')
section
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12
        .text-center
          h4.mb-5.type--uppercase Why Excide
        p.lead.m32 At Excide, we will advise you through the entire fund raising process by providing detailed forecast models. We will advise you on how much to fund raise dependent on sensitive scenarios and also help to determine which investor/bank is most probable. We are committed in getting you the best deal from these investors and its company. We will help you through:
        ul.lead data-bullet="ti-check-box"
          li Evaluation of requirements
          li Liaise and negotiate
          li Investor/Bank meetings
section.imagebg.overlay
  .background-image-holder
    img.background-image alt="image" src=image_path('table-top-post-its.jpg')
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-12.text-center
        h3.type--uppercase.mb-5.mb-xs-32 More Services
        = render 'services_list'
section#contactus
  .container
    .row.mb--2
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12.text-center
        h4.mb-5.type--uppercase Need to know more about what we offer?
        p.lead.mb80 There is nothing like a face-to-face meeting to better understand each other. Leave your details below and we will get in touch with you soon.
    = render 'contact'